          "parodyTraps": "Autopilot heartbreak clichés and numbness tropes the user never wrote; vowel-mush lines with no concrete image (pretty sound, says nothing); every line the exact same length in a singsong lull; sad-boy costume on a story that is not sad. Real melodic rap earns the ache with one specific detail; parody just moans in tune.",
